Package: SigfoxTagPrep
Title: Download, Process, and Analyse Sigfox Wildlife Tracking Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Edward", "Hurme", , "edwardhurme@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2936-2449"))
Description: Tools for working with ICARUS/Sigfox wildlife tracking tags
    (TinyFox, NanoFox, uWasp). Provides functions to download raw transmission
    data from the MPIAB Sigfox database or Movebank, convert it to move2
    objects, compute movement metrics (speed, distance, bearing, displacement,
    VeDBA), add environmental covariates from ERA5 rasters, detect tag
    fall-off events, and identify continuous nocturnal flight bouts.
